verbose_text: The following data were analyzed : age; sex; mechanism and circumstances of death; cause of death; blood ethanol concentration at the time of death, whether or not the person was hospitalized; number of days the person survived after sustaining trauma; whether or not there were injuries to the chest and abdomen or pelvis; vertebral fractures in the cervical, thoracic, and lumbar spine; and the presence or lack of TTPFs.
evidence: age; sex; mechanism and circumstances of death; cause of death
